univention-samba (5.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * exit in join script if the net rpc join fails. Bug #7081
  * remove old pdc-takeover script. Bug #10660
  * added UCR variable samba/passdb/expand/explicit to set 'passdb
    expand explicit'. Bug #10680
  * sync netlogon share during join. Bug #16492
  * remove the invalid users UCR settings which was set in earlier UCS
    installations. Bug #16687
  * use samba/user binddn for unix password sync script on a memberser
    as on a dc slave if package slave-pdc is installed. Bug #16701
  * register samba/password/checkscript for 81univention-samba_scripts.
    Bug #17163
  * change the default for wide links from 'yes' to 'no'. Bug #17593
  * added UCR variable samba/cups/encrypt to control whether connections
    to CUPS servers will be encrypted or not. Bug #18425

 -- Stefan Gohmann <gohmann@univention.de>  Wed, 26 May 2010 21:22:03 +0200

